query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.categoryId, c.name as category_name, c.parentId
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.categoryId = c.id
WHERE p.status = 'published'
ORDER BY p.categoryId
LIMIT 10;
